org.nasdanika.codegen.ecore.web.ui.model

Interface EClassConfiguration

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CDOObject, CDOWithID, EModelElementConfiguration, ENamedElementConfiguration, EObject, Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EClassConfigurationImpl

    public interface EClassConfiguration
extends ENamedElementConfiguration

    A representation of the model object ‘EClass Configuration’.

    The following features are supported:

    • Dispatch Features
    • Label
    • View Item
    • Horizontal Form
    • Novalidate
    • Feature Items Container
    • Feature Items Container Configuration
    See Also:
    ModelPackage.getEClassConfiguration()

    • Method Detail

      • isDispatchFeatures

        boolean isDispatchFeatures()

        Returns the value of the ‘Dispatch Features’ attribute. If set to true, the generator generates renderfeature nameFeatureXXX(C,T,EStructuralFeature,…) and overrides renderFeatureXXX(C,T,EStructuralFeature,…) to dispatch invocations to feature-specific methods. This does not alter the default renderer behavior, but makes the variability points explicit and easier to customize.

        Returns:
        the value of the ‘Dispatch Features’ attribute.
        See Also:
        setDispatchFeatures(boolean), ModelPackage.getEClassConfiguration_DispatchFeatures()

      • isNovalidate

        boolean isNovalidate()

        Returns the value of the ‘Novalidate’ attribute. The default value is “false”. Set to true to disable HTML 5 form validation, e.g. if you have a required text area with TinyMCE editor in Chrome.

      • getFeatureItemsContainerConfiguration

        String getFeatureItemsContainerConfiguration()

        Returns the value of the ‘Feature Items Container Configuration’ attribute. The default value is "". Feature items container configuration.

        For accordion:

        • style: Bootstrap style, e.g. PRIMARY

        For pills:

        • stacked: true or false
        • justified: true or false
        • width: 1 - 11

        For tabs:

        • justified: true or false
        Returns:
        the value of the ‘Feature Items Container Configuration’ attribute.
        See Also:
        setFeatureItemsContainerConfiguration(String), ModelPackage.getEClassConfiguration_FeatureItemsContainerConfiguration()
